N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1261.25 - Permission to land or take-off jet or turbo-prop aircraft required

State Regulations

No jet or turbo-prop aircraft may land or take-off at
an air terminal without permission. Notes
